<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="b30Sep1938"><font color="red">30 September 1938</font> <i>NLVP</i> (from Ben Huebsch to Paul L&eacute;on): I have now consulted with Messrs Faber and Faber and we have arrived at satisfactory arrangements for producing the forthcoming Joyce book in such a way as to save Joyce from examining another set of proofs and yet protect his United States copyright. </div>
